feature, so best thing to do is to go to the Bookdone book documentation, and you will find

00:49:39.919 --> 00:49:46.560
the part about Word documents, and this, maybe I can paste the link if I find it quick.

00:49:48.159 --> 00:49:49.040
This will be here.

