00:51:25.679 --> 00:51:32.639
This is a package that allows to write RMD and embed it to image, but the difficult part is that

00:51:32.639 --> 00:51:38.800
if you want to embed something into an email, everything needs to be contained into the email,

00:51:38.800 --> 00:51:45.280
and Plotly is pretty big, so I don't know if this is possible, but really, I don't know the answer,

00:51:45.280 --> 00:51:52.800
so it could be from a colleague of mine, but you should, like, try with the Blastula package,

00:51:53.199 --> 00:51:58.080
and if it doesn't work, look into the issue or ask the question in the community,

00:51:58.719 --> 00:52:03.199
and Rich will surely answer to you.

