00:59:00.959 --> 00:59:08.159
in French. And so, for that, you need to add an attribute which is, I think, this one.

00:59:09.120 --> 00:59:12.479
I'm posting in the Zoom site in the YAML.

00:59:16.479 --> 00:59:24.879
This one to change the language of HTML. But this is an HTML thing. So, this would not work

00:59:24.879 --> 00:59:30.719
for PDF, for example, or would have no usage. Or maybe it works. I don't know. It is different. But

00:59:31.439 --> 00:59:37.040
if the issue you have is in the output, maybe it's an HTML configuration and not the Armagnan

